item.description:
@mr_extremez wrote:

You can always just add all the doors:

case 1516: case 1519: case 13001: case 1530: case 2307: case 2308: case 12349: case 12350: case 1536: case 1533: case 12986: case 12987: case 1553: case 1551: case 7049: case 7050: case 1591: case 59: case 11707: case 11714: case 2398: case 2051: case 2050: case 1558: case 1557: case 3390: case 3391: case 1508: case 1506: case 2551: case 2550: case 2556: case 9330: case 2054: case 2546: case 2548: case 1722: case 9302: case 5889: case 5893: case 5887: case 5891: case 4800: case 1596: case 1597: case 2862: case 2861: case 1512: case 9299: c.getPA().object(-1, obX, obY, 0, 0); //Delete Door new Object(-1, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel, 0, 10, -1, 0); break;

Shantay/al kharid:

[code]case 2882:
case 2883:
if(c.getItems().playerHasItem(995, 5)) {
c.getItems().deleteItem2(995, 5);
c.getPA().object(-1, obX, obY, 0, 0); //Delete Door
new Object(-1, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel, 0, 10, -1, 0);
c.sendMessage(“You pass the Gate.”);
} else {
c.sendMessage(“You need 5 coins to pass this gate!”);
}
break;

case 4031:
if(c.getItems().playerHasItem(1854, 1)) {
c.getItems().deleteItem2(1854, 1);
c.getPA().object(-1, obX, obY, 0, 0); //Delete Door
new Object(-1, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel, 0, 10, -1, 0);
c.sendMessage(“You pass the Gate.”);
} else {
c.sendMessage(“You need a shantay pass to pass this gate!”);
}
break;[/code]

Guilds if you want:

[code]case 1805: //Champions Guild
if (c.questPoints >= 33) {
Server.objectHandler.doorHandling(objectType, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel);
c.sendMessage(“You enter the guild of Champions.”);
} else {
c.sendMessage(“You must have at least 33 quest points to enter this Guild!”);
}
break;

	case 2641:	//Monastery (Prayer)
		if (c.playerLevel[c.playerPrayer] > 31) {
			c.getPA().movePlayer(3057, 3484, 1);	
			c.sendMessage("You enter the guild of Monks.");
		} else {
			c.sendMessage("You must have a Prayer level of 31 to enter this Section of the Monastery!");
		}
		break;
	
	case 2624:
	case 2625:	//Heroes' Guild
			Server.objectHandler.doorHandling(objectType, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel);
			c.sendMessage("You enter the guild of Heroes.");
			c.sendMessage("[Coming Soon] Heroes Quest.");
		break;
	
	case 15653:	//Warrriors Guild
		if (c.playerLevel[c.playerAttack] + c.playerLevel[c.playerStrength] >= 130 || c.playerLevel[c.playerAttack] > 99 || c.playerLevel[c.playerStrength] > 99 ) {
			Server.objectHandler.doorHandling(objectType, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel);		
			c.sendMessage("You enter the guild of Warriors.");
		} else {
			c.sendMessage("You must have a Attack or Strength level of 99 to enter this Guild!");
			c.sendMessage("Or a Attack & Strength level combination of 130.");
		}
		break;
	
	case 2391:
	case 2392:	//Legends Guild
			Server.objectHandler.doorHandling(objectType, c.objectX, c.objectY, 0);	
			c.sendMessage("You enter the guild of Legends.");
			c.sendMessage("[Coming Soon] Legends Quest.");
		break;
		
	case 2712:	//Cooking Guild
		if (c.playerLevel[c.playerCooking] > 32 && c.getItems().playerHasItem(1949, 1) || c.getItems().playerHasItem(9801, 1) || c.getItems().playerHasItem(9802, 1) ) {
			Server.objectHandler.doorHandling(objectType, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel);
			c.sendMessage("You enter the guild of Cooks.");
		} else {
			c.sendMessage("You must have a Cooking level of 32 to enter this Guild!");
			c.sendMessage("You must also have a Chefs hat or a Cooking cape.");
		}
		break;
		
	case 2647:	//Crafting Guild
		if (c.playerLevel[c.playerCrafting] > 40 && c.getItems().playerHasItem(1757, 1) || c.getItems().playerHasItem(9780, 1) || c.getItems().playerHasItem(9781, 1) ) {
			Server.objectHandler.doorHandling(objectType, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel);
			c.sendMessage("You enter the guild of Crafters.");
		} else {
			c.sendMessage("You must have a Crafting level of 40 to enter this Guild!");
			c.sendMessage("You must also have a Brown Apron or a Crafting Cape.");
		}
		break;
		
	case 2113:	//Mining Guild
		if (c.playerLevel[c.playerMining] > 60) {
			c.getPA().movePlayer(3021, 9739, 0);
			c.sendMessage("You enter the guild of Miners.");
		} else {
			c.sendMessage("You must have a Mining level of 60 to enter this Guild!");
		}
		break;
		
	case 2025:	//Fishing Guild
		if (c.playerLevel[c.playerFishing] > 68) {
			Server.objectHandler.doorHandling(objectType, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel);
			c.sendMessage("You enter the guild of Fishermen.");
		} else {
			c.sendMessage("You must have a Fishing level of 68 to enter this Guild!");
		}
		break;
		
	case 1600:
	case 1601:	//Wizards Guild
		if (c.playerLevel[c.playerMagic] > 66) {
			Server.objectHandler.doorHandling(objectType, c.objectX, c.objectY, c.heightLevel);
			c.sendMessage("You enter the guild of Wizard's.");
		} else {
			c.sendMessage("You must have a Magic level of 66 to enter this Guild!");
		}
		break;
		
	case 2514:	//Ranging Guild
		if (c.playerLevel[c.playerRanged] > 40 && c.absX == 2658 && c.absY == 3437 || c.absX == 2659 && c.absY == 3438) {
				c.getPA().movePlayer(2657, 3439, 0);
		} else if (c.absX == 2658 && c.absY == 3439 || c.absX == 2657 && c.absY == 3438) {
				c.getPA().movePlayer(2659, 3437, 0);
		} else {
			c.sendMessage("You must have a Ranged level of 40 to enter this Guild!");
			c.sendMessage("Or you need to move closer to the door to enter.");
		}
		break;[/code]
